<plot>A lonely woman is driving on a dark road, she stops to fill up with gasoline, and she also goes to the toilet. When she hits the road again a big truck puts on all his lights and follows her. No matter how fast she's driving, the truck follows her. She tries to phone the police on her cellular phone, but the phone goes dead - because of the batteries. She is driving faster and faster out into the middle of nowhere...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104150</url></doc>
